            <Title>CiteTools Integration</Title>
            <Text>By Bernardo Vasconcelos (see this thread)

This is a short summary of changes to Ian's excellect Quarto template for Scrivener to integrate the Cite Tools Quarto Extension. The extension introduces bibliography features that previously had been confined to BibTeX to Pandoc's Citeproc environment, keeping the output consistent across most formats (LaTeX, DOCX, HTML, and so on).

Install the extension to your Quarto project or to the  export-mmd folder you are using.

quarto install extension bcdavasconcelos/citetools</Text>
            <Notes>For the project to compile you'll have to:

brew install xquartz
brew install librsvg
</Notes>
